nodes.text: Stang was an expletive originating on Alderaan. It became popular among people of the galaxy. Anakin Skywalker used the word frequently during his and Obi-Wan Kenobi's mission to Lanteeb. Other notable Jedi, including Mara Jade Skywalker, her son Ben Skywalker and his cousin Jaina Solo Fel have also used this word frequently.
